14
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:35,080
(Adapted from the serialized work "Reborn"
by Qiang Yu)

15
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,156
(CD4+ T-cell levels
have returned to normal range.)

16
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:41,320
Qiao Beiyu passed away
on Lunar New Year's Eve last year.

17
00:01:41,940 --> 00:01:44,530
But according to the record,

18
00:01:45,610 --> 00:01:47,690
in December the year before that,

19
00:01:47,890 --> 00:01:50,660
her condition was stable
in every aspect.

20
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:55,380
She went from stabilizing

21
00:01:55,380 --> 00:01:57,460
to passing away in less than two months.

22
00:01:57,530 --> 00:01:58,660
That's way too fast.

23
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:01,530
Do you think Beiyu's death

24
00:02:01,690 --> 00:02:03,330
wasn't inevitable,

25
00:02:03,580 --> 00:02:04,820
but rather a choice?

26
00:02:06,180 --> 00:02:08,890
What do you mean?

27
00:02:08,890 --> 00:02:10,240
Did Mom and Dad stop the treatment

28
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,540
because they couldn't afford it?

29
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,420
Can you give it a rest already?

30
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:16,180
Don't forget what you did to Jinrui.

31
00:02:16,180 --> 00:02:18,330
Stop stirring up more trouble.

32
